      </div>

      <!-- Small Countdown Repeat (Optional) -->
      <div class="mt-8">
        <p class="text-white/80 text-sm">
          ‚è∞ El curso comienza en <span id="countdown-days-small" class="font-bold">--</span> d√≠as
        </p>
